@SysInclude { doc }
@Doc @Text @Begin
@PP
The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog -- text intended for
the OpenType smcp (small-caps) feature.  Phase 1 records the GSUB
substitution table on CFF/OTF fonts but does not yet rewrite the
emitted codepoints, so both back-ends render plain lower-case here.
@End @Text
